SAP,Anywhere,provides,APIs,Application,Programming,Interface,for,integrating,SAP,Anywhere,with,third,party,applications,With,these,APIs,you,can,extract,your,data,in,SAP,Anywhere,in,the,JSON,format,and,develop,new,applications,or,integrate,with,your,existing,business,applications,The,SAP,Anywhere,APIs,are,built,on,top,of,the,OAuth,protocol,and,follow,the,REST,principle,All,the,requests,to,the,APIs,can,be,easily,performed,with,the,curl,command,line,tool,or,the,Postman,Google,Chrome,app